quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  16,27,"Refti ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, Alla hoyniroyay ﾉ兎 lepte, O jaasinira ﾉ兎 ﾉ容, O daalana ﾉ兎: Ko honto ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁 kafidaynoﾉ熔n e am ka dewe, ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁 haﾉ妬raynoﾉ熔n Annabaaﾉ兎 e gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 fii mun? Joomiraaﾉ兎 gannde ﾉ擁gguﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'a: Koyeera e lepte ﾉ容n ﾃ疎lnde Darnal, yanay e heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  16,28,"ﾆ‘n ﾉ兎 Malaa'ikaajo waroowo on e wallondirooﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n ﾆｴettitata ruuhuuji maﾉ橡兎, hara ko ﾉ兎 jillondirﾉ兎 e tooﾃｱirgol ko'e maﾉ橡兎 yeddugol Alla. ﾆ‘ jebbiloo ko ﾉ兎 yankinaniiﾉ兎 maayde yanunde e maﾉ橡兎 nden, ﾉ兎 yedda keeferaaku e geddi ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 wonunoo e mun, sikkugol ﾉ蓉m nafay ﾉ兎. ﾆ‘ wi'a- nee ontuma: On fenay, pellet hari ko on heeferﾉ兎 yeddunooﾉ兎. Pellet Alla no anndi ko huuwaynoﾉ熔n aduna, huunde suuﾉ預aki Mo e ﾉ蓉m, O yoﾉ妬toyay on ﾉ蓉m."
  16,29,"ﾆ‘ wi'anee: Naatiree dame Jahannama ﾉ容n emmbere kuuﾉ容 mon ﾉ容n, ko on luttooﾉ兎 ton poomaa. Nge bonii ﾃｱaaﾆｴorde wonande townitiiﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁ngol Alla rewa Mo Kanko tun."
  16,30,"Wi'anee ﾉ兎n hulirﾉ兎 Joomi maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ熔ftagol yamirooje Makko ﾉ容n woﾉ遼擁too e haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n: Ko honﾉ蓉m Joomi mon jippini e Annabaajo mon on Muhammadu (yo o his)? ﾆ‘ jaaboo: Ko moﾆｴﾆｴere mawnde Alla jippini e makko. Hino woodani ﾉ兎n moﾆｴﾆｴimﾉ兎 rewugol Alla ngol ﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴini huuwondiral maﾉ橡兎 ngal e tagu Makko ngun aduna ﾉ熔o mbarjaari labaandi: wano ballal e yaajireede arsike. Ko ko Alla marani ﾉ兎 kon e mbarjaari ka laakara ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude diini ndin ndi O yaccinani ﾉ兎 ka aduna. Saare laakara nden moﾆｴﾆｴanii hulirﾉ兎 Joomi mun ﾉ熔ftagol yamirooje Makko ﾉ容n woﾉ遼擁too haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n."
  16,31,"Aljanaaji ﾃｱiiﾉ殿l e duumal ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 naatata, canﾉ擁 no ila senngo ley kuﾉ兎eje e leﾉ遼容 majji. Hino woodani ﾉ兎 e ﾉ擁n Aljannaaji, kala ko wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 tuuyetee e ﾃｱaametee e njaram ekw. Ko wano ndii njoﾉ電i ndi Alla yoﾉ妬tiri gmﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e mofte Muhammadu (jom-kisiyee) ﾉ容n, O yoﾉ妬tirta gomﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 e mofte adinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  16,32,"ﾆ‘n ﾉ兎 Malaa'ikaajo waroowo on e wallondirooﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n ﾆｴettitata -hara ko ﾉ兎 laaﾉ砥ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎rﾉ容 mun e keeferaaku- Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'ana ﾉ兎: Salaamun 窶和laykum (kisiyee wonii e mon), on hisii e kala geddi. Naatiree Alajanna on sabu ko golli-raynoﾉ熔n kon ka aduna, immorde e fiﾉ渡de sellunde e golle moﾆｴﾆｴe."
  16,33,"Hara ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎 fenna hino habbitii si wanaa ﾉ兎 Malaa'ikaajo waroowo on e wallondirooﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n arata e maﾉ橡兎 fii hunnugol ﾉ兎 pittaali ﾉ擁n, piya geece maﾉ橡兎 e ﾉ殿bbe maﾉ橡兎, maa yamiroore Alla gasnirgol ﾉ兎 lepte ﾉ容n aduna ara? Ko wano ﾉ容e kuuﾉ容 ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎 Makka ﾉ熔o ﾉ兎ya sirkooﾉ兎 adinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 huuwunoo haa Alla halki ﾉ兎. Alla tooﾃｱiraano ﾉ兎 ngol halkugol ﾉ兎; si ko woni, ko ko'e maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎 wonunoo toopirde ukkoragol e ko halkirta ﾉ兎 kon yeddugol Alla."
  16,34,"Lepte boneeji kuuﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容 ﾉ兎 huuwaynoo ﾉ容n jippii e maﾉ橡兎, lepte ﾉ容n ﾉ容 ﾉ兎 jalkitaynoo si ﾉ兎 waajoraama ﾉ容 yani e maﾉ橡兎."